Date: 1992-09-08

Title: Quantum Soliton Mass Corrections in SL(N) Affine Toda Theory

Authors: Timothy Hollowood

Comments: 14 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B300 (1993) 73-83

The first quantum mass corrections for the solitons of complex $sl(n)$ affineToda field theory are calculated. The corrections are real and preserve theclassical mass ratios. The formalism also proves that the solitons areclassically stable.